{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Add categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata -->
{{tsh|wtc}}

Makes a box linking to a category of Wiktionary.

== Usage ==
*code: {{tnull|Wiktionary category 2}} 
*Result: 
{{Wiktionary category 2}}
{{clear}}

*code: {{tnull|Wiktionary category 2|Terms derived from Hungarian}}
*Result: 
{{Wiktionary category 2|Terms derived from Hungarian}}
{{clear}}

== See also ==
{{Wiktionary templates common doc}}

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Interwiki category linking templates]]
[[Category:Wiktionary link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

